org.ctoolkit.restapi.client

Interface Request<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the resource type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ListRetrievalRequest<T>, PayloadRequest<T>, RetrievalRequest<T>, SimpleRequest<T>

    public interface Request<T>
    The top level request wrapper to provide possibility to isolate a remote call to standalone object.
    Author:
    Aurel Medvegy

        T finish(@Nonnull
       RequestCredential credential)

        Parameters:
